name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForPeripheralVascularDisease
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Peripheral Vascular Disease
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to peripheral vascular disease and is listed as a cardiovascular disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes peripheral vascular disease. It includes extremity ischemia and peripheral angiopathy.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
